title: Chilliwack - Gone, Gone, Gone (2009)
description:
Chilliwack - Gone, Gone, Gone 1969-2003 (2009)

A definitive 2CD Chilliwack anthology containing 41 songs.  For those that only know the big hits, this makes a great introduction.

Disc One
1. My Girl (Gone, Gone, Gone) / 2. Fly at Night (In The morning we land) / 3. Don't Stop / 4. Lonesome Mary (LP Version) / 5. (We Don't Have To) Fall In Love / 6. There's Something I Like About That (LP Version) / 7. Raino (Short Version) / 8. Tonight / 9. If you want my love / 10. Something Better (Single Version) / 11. I wanna be the one / 12. Got You On My Mind / 13. Riding High / 14. Arms Of Mary / 15. Chain Train (Single Version) / 16. How Can You Hide your love / 17. Come On Over (Single Version) / 18. Mr. Rock / 19. Ground Hog / 20. She Keeps On Cryin' / 21. Secret Information

Disc Two
1. Whatcha Gonna Do (When I'm gone) (LP Version) / 2. I Believe (LP Version) / 3. Last Day Of December / 4. Communication Breakdown (LP version) / 5. Road To Paradise / 6. Baby Blue (LP Version) / 7. Ridin' (LP Version) / 8. Ride-out / 9. Tell It To The Telephone / 10. Crazy Talk (Short Version) / 11. Sundown (Single Version) / 12. Don't It Make You Feel Good / 13. Gettin' Better / 14. Seventeenth Summer / 15. Trial By Fire (Live) / 16. California Girl (LP Version) / 17. Patent On The Wind / 18. Singin' The Blues (All Over You) / 19. Sleep Music / 20. Fly At Night (Reprise)

Sources: Mostly vinyl, some CDs.  160/JS/MP3.
